{"id":1232,"date":"2025-04-12T00:09:14","date_gmt":"2025-04-11T17:09:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1232"},"modified":"2025-12-14T10:11:11","modified_gmt":"2025-12-14T03:11:11","slug":"tach-day-phi-kim-seo","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tach-day-phi-kim-seo\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1y v\u00e0 phi kim s\u1eb9o"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t cho da s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u00f3ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m \u0111\u00e1y vu\u00f4ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng ch\u00e2n kim.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da do s\u1eb9o g\u00e2y n\u00ean.<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba nguy c\u01a1 t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t s\u1eb9o, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf s\u1eb9o l\u00e2u n\u0103m.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da v\u00f9ng s\u1eb9o, tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da v\u00e0 thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1y ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 c\u00e1c s\u1ee3i li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u1eb9o, m\u00f4 s\u1eb9o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea7y gi\u00fap li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh phi kim s\u1eb9o chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Phi kim si\u00eau vi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhanh h\u01a1n g\u1ea5p 3 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi b\u00f4i thoa tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/li>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng song song c\u00f9ng GSC Ultra Calming K Cream ch\u1ee9a ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n (Pro Anti-Irritant Complex) g\u1ed3m Vitamin K, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t c\u00fac La M\u00e3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt gi\u00fap l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh nhanh t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da s\u1eb9o t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, m\u1edd th\u00e2m, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da, t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 01 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ebfn 02 ti\u1ebfng.<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 &#8211; 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 2px; top: 367px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t cho da s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u00f3ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m \u0111\u00e1y vu\u00f4ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng ch\u00e2n kim.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3561,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[34],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1232","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-microneedling","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1232","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1232"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/medi